bug.short_desc: 4.7.2 kernel upgrade fails output to display with Intel GM45
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1197728 this is what I get after boot
Description of problem: Display has no output since upgrading to 4.7.2 kernel from 4.6.*
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
How reproducible: Every kernel boot with no edit to boot parameters
Steps to Reproduce: 1.Boot & select 4.7.2 kernel 2.n/a 3.n/a
Actual results: no output on display
Expected results: RGB interface on LVDS1 (just being techie there!)
Additional info: 4.7.2 works if nomodeset is inserted to boot command (with restricted graphical result!)
Intel Corporation 82801 Mobile PCI Bridge
id: display:0 description: VGA compatible controller product: Mobile 4 Series Chipset Integrated Graphics Controller [8086:2A42] vendor: Intel Corporation [8086] physical id: 2 bus info: pci@0000:00:02.0 version: 07 width: 64 bits clock: 33MHz capabilities: msi pm vga_controller bus_master cap_list
